92w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Henry-Cavill-Warhammer-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>巫师本人亨利·卡维尔对<em>战锤</em>新游戏<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/warhammer-40k-space-marine-2"><em>《星际战士2》</em></a>给予了高度评价。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/has-gaming-outpriced-the-average-player-3795266">游戏的价格是否超过了普通玩家？</a></strong></li></ul><p>亨利·卡维尔是<em>《战锤》的</em>忠实粉丝。 2022 年， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/henry-cavill-surprises-customers-during-visit-to-nottingham-warhammer-store-3165071">他在参观诺丁汉<em>战锤</em></a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/henry-cavill-surprises-customers-during-visit-to-nottingham-warhammer-store-3165071">商店</a>时给顾客带来了惊喜，同年晚些时候宣布他将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/henry-cavill-to-star-in-and-produce-new-warhammer-series-for-amazon-3368549">主演并为亚马逊制作一个新的<em>战锤</em></a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/henry-cavill-to-star-in-and-produce-new-warhammer-series-for-amazon-3368549">系列</a>。</p><p>据<em><a href="https://www.pcgamer.com/games/third-person-shooter/henry-cavill-is-a-big-space-marine-2-fan-loving-the-pvp-and-am-really-looking-forward-to-it-growing-and-expanding/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PCGamer</a>报道，</em>卡维尔在他的 Instagram 帐户上发布了<em>《星际战士 2》</em>的相关信息，并写道：“这款游戏是杂种狗的……不过，说实话，他们做得相当不错吧？我无法独自完成《死亡天使》的战役（或者至少没有耐心独自完成！），但我很喜欢！” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DAQkdyno98l/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex